m_q.target_metric: Whether 'Other' reports were more than half of total reports in any year between 2001-2024
sub_questions: Calculate total reports per year (sum of Fraud, Identity Theft, Other)
Calculate proportion of Other reports per year
Check if proportion > 0.5 for any year in range

format_notes: First column is Year, subsequent columns are report type counts

constraints: All count columns should be non-negative integers
Total reports = Fraud + Identity Theft + Other > 0
